	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Kingston Jamaica</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>Janry 7th 1859</date></p>
				<p>Dear <addressee>Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I have received your esteemed<lb/> favor together with the books which I shall<lb/> endeavor to dispose of as early as<lb/> possible.  I understand that a <persName>Mr. Joseph</persName><lb/> is selling books of the same description at<lb/> &#36;2 piece&#44; however&#44; I shall do the best I can<lb/> for you&#44; so that you shall not <sic>loose</sic> by them<lb/> it will not answer for me to send the first nos of the magazine to any one as is customary with<lb/> your publishers for I will not suffer any book<lb/> to go out of my hands without the cash being paid<lb/> for them as there is no dependence on any one in<lb/> <placeName>Jamaica</placeName>.  Nothing but Poverty every where&#44; I<lb/> notice the different deaths and except <persName>Mrs. <del>Hk</del><lb/> Hackenburgh</persName> is what <persName>Lex Liebe<add>&#63;</add></persName>&#44; give my<lb/> love to <persName>Louisa</persName>&#44; and say I have received her letter<lb/> but could not answer by this opportunity.</p>
				<p>Remember me kindly to <persName>Mrs. Cousens</persName> &#38; the<lb/> family&#44; <del>In</del> as well as all friends.  In the hope<lb/> that you are completely recoverd &#38; enjoying health</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I remain <add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Your friend</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">A. C. Peirpotte</persName></p>
				<p>The book given as a sample<lb/> was the same as those sent now.<lb/> <add>&#63;</add> <persName>LD Lufus<add>&#63;</add></persName> remembers<lb/> Kindly to you all.</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">pr <persName>William Thompson</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">via <placeName>New Orleans</placeName></p>
		</body>
